Package nz.ac.vuw.ecs.swen225.gp20.maze

Class Maze

  • java.lang.Object
    • nz.ac.vuw.ecs.swen225.gp20.maze.Maze
  • public class Maze
extends java.lang.Object
    From Handout: The game state is primarily made up of the maze itself, the current location of Chap on the maze, the treasure chest and other items Chap has collected, such as keys. The game logic controls what events may, or may not happen in the game world (e.g. “Can Chap go through this door?”, “Can Chap pick up this object?”, “Does this key open that door?”, etc.).

    The core logic of the game is that the player moves Chap around the maze until he reaches the exit and then advances to the next level (if there is another level). This module should make extensive use of contracts to ensure the integrity of the maze.
